c74object.name: fl.untag~
c74object.digest: Separates vectors from a tagged frame according to a given set of tags.
c74object.description: A variable number of outputs is available, each of which deal will a specific tag. The number of outputs is specified either explicitly with a parameter or implicitly by which arguments or tag parameters are present.

entry.name: 0. /num_outs [instantiation int]
entry.description: Sets the number of outputs (and hence the number of tags.

entry.name: 1. /tag_01 [instantiation string]
entry.description: Sets the tag related to output 1.
